translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,53,Aey humaray paalney walay mabood! Hum teri utari hui wahee per eman laye aur hum ney teray rasool ki ittaba ki pus tu humen gawahon mein likh ley
  3,54,Aur kafiron ney makar kiya aur Allah Taalaa ney bhi (makar) khufiya tadbeer ki aur Allah Taalaa sab khufiya tadbeer kerney walon say behtar hai
  3,55,Jab Allah Taalaa ney farmaya kay aey essa! Mein tujhay poora lenay wala hun aur tujhay apni janib uthaney wala hun aur tujhay kafiron say pak kerney wala hun aur teray tabeydaron ko kafiron kay upper ghalib kerney wala hun qayamat kay din tak phir tum sab ka lotna meri hi taraf hai mein hi tumharay aapas kay tamam tar ikhtilafaat ka faisla keroon ga
  3,56,Phir kafiron ko to mein duniya aur aakhirat mein sakhta tar azab doon ga aur unn ka koi madadgar na hoga
  3,57,Lekin eman walon aur nek aemaal logon ko Allah Taalaa unn ka sawab poora poora dey ga aur Allah Taalaa zalimon say mohabbat nahi kerta
  3,58,Yeh jisay hum teray samney parh rahey hain aayaten hain aur hikmar wali naseehat hain
  3,59,Allah Taalaa kay nazdeek essa (alh-e-salam) ki misal hoo ba hoo aadam (alh-e-salam) ki misal hai jissay mitti say bana ker keh diya kay ho ja! Pus woh hogaya
  3,60,Teray rab ki taraf say haq yehi hai khabardar shak kerney walon mein say na hona
  3,61,Iss liye jo shaks aap kay pass iss ilm kay aajaney kay baad bhi aap say iss mein jhagray to aap keh den kay aao hum tum apney apney farzandon ko aur hum tum apni apni aurton ko aur hum tum khas apni apni janon ko bula len phir hum aajzi kay sath iltija keren aur jhooton per Allah ki laanat keren